{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Recreate Northumbria and grant it nation status",
        "additional_details": "We need the government to help us get the ability to vote for our nation status and to gain it so we have our own Northumbrian government and our own country within the UK.",
        "background": "We believe Yorkshire, Durham, Tyne and Wear, Cumbria and Northumberland should come to together and be Northumbria again. We believe being a part of England has limited us so much and having a bit of independence and leaving England to be our own nation within the UK will be the best for us.",
